<font color=#FFFF00>-Jika kau...
- Ya.</font>

910
00:58:10,644 --> 00:58:12,814
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak bisa tidur,</font>

911
00:58:13,144 --> 00:58:15,314
<font color=#FFFF00>pikirkan saja aku ada di sampingmu...</font>

912
00:58:16,584 --> 00:58:17,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Terserah kau.</font>

913
00:58:20,744 --> 00:58:22,484
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kau temani aku?</font>

914
00:58:23,684 --> 00:58:24,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, tidak bisa!</font>

915
00:58:50,884 --> 00:58:52,614
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

916
00:59:59,444 --> 01:00:01,014
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian terlihat manis bersama.</font>

917
01:00:11,984 --> 01:00:13,784
<font color=#FFFF00>(Diary Bong Hee)</font>

918
01:00:15,384 --> 01:00:17,344
<font color=#FFFF00>(Yang paling aku cintai di
dunia ini, Park Young Soon.)</font>

919
01:00:17,684 --> 01:00:19,914
<font color=#FFFF00>(Bong Hee kecil.)</font>

920
01:00:24,984 --> 01:00:26,984
<font color=#FFFF00>(Dengan ayah tercintaku.)</font>

921
01:00:32,984 --> 01:00:34,044
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

922
01:00:35,814 --> 01:00:36,884
<font color=#FFFF00>Mimpi indah, ya.</font>

923
01:00:43,908 --> 01:00:48,908
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Translated by @oohthifa</b></font>

924
01:01:20,896 --> 01:01:22,326
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau dapat yang depan,
