925
01:01:22,396 --> 01:01:23,766
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau yang belakang, aku takkan.</font>

926
01:01:34,966 --> 01:01:35,966
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

927
01:01:35,966 --> 01:01:37,166
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terus melakukan itu seharian.</font>

928
01:01:37,166 --> 01:01:38,766
<font color=#FFFF00>Suaranya berisik.
Apa ini?</font>

929
01:01:38,766 --> 01:01:40,396
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau mengotak-atiknya seharian?</font>

930
01:01:40,496 --> 01:01:41,766
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan sudah.</font>

931
01:01:47,466 --> 01:01:48,466
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga!</font>

932
01:01:48,466 --> 01:01:50,066
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, ini...</font>

